I am a final year Ph.D. student at IIT Hyderabad. I am advised by [https://www.iith.ac.in/~vineethnb/ Prof. Vineeth N Balasubramanian]. I work on the research problems at the intersection of Causality and AI. I like to play chess and write [https://amruthavarshni.blogspot.com/ poems] (mostly in Telugu) in my free time.
